data.description: Great opportunity to purchase rare split-level home in quiet neighborhood of Coventry. Upstairs boasts three bedrooms and a full bath as well as comfortable living room complete with cozy fireplace right off kitchen/dining area.  Also, a bonus Florida room off of kitchen for added living space. The downstairs is set up as a large family Den currently with a half bathroom as well. Bringing a little love to this 1970 house would really turn it into a home. Fenced in yard! Subject to seller finding suitable housing.
